<template>
  <v-card>
    ScatterPlot goes here
  </v-card>
</template>


<script>
import * as echarts from 'echarts'
export default {
  name: "ScatterPlot",
  data() {return{
  }},
  mounted() {
    this.drawScatterPlot()
  },
  methods: {
    drawScatterPlot(){
      var chartDom = document.getElementById('main');
      var myChart = echarts.init(chartDom);
      var option;

      option = {
        xAxis: {},
        yAxis: {},
        series: [
          {
            symbolSize: 20,
            data: [
              [10.0, 8.04],
              [8.07, 6.95],
              [13.0, 7.58],
              [9.05, 8.81],
              [11.0, 8.33],
              [14.0, 7.66],
              [13.4, 6.81],
              [10.0, 6.33],
              [14.0, 8.96],
              [12.5, 6.82],
              [9.15, 7.2],
              [11.5, 7.2],
              [3.03, 4.23],
              [12.2, 7.83],
              [2.02, 4.47],
              [1.05, 3.33],
              [4.05, 4.96],
              [6.03, 7.24],
              [12.0, 6.26],
              [12.0, 8.84],
              [7.08, 5.82],
              [5.02, 5.68]
            ],
            type: 'scatter'
          }
        ]
      };

      option && myChart.setOption(option);
    }
  }
}

</script>
